&lt;/style&gt;&lt;/head&gt;&lt;body style=" font-family:'MS Shell Dlg 2'; font-size:8.25pt; font-weight:400; font-style:normal;"&gt;
&lt;p style=" margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px; margin-left:0px; margin-right:0px; -qt-block-indent:0; text-indent:0px;"&gt;sim900 generic one instance of the generic (i.e. not one of the Seeed boards) sim900 modules. It matches the specific board this person has but may do for the general generic sim900 modules.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/body&gt;&lt;/html&gt;</description>
